<h3 class="regularSummaryHeadline"><a target="_blank" href="/technology/20200515/trump-tsmc-us-chip-facility/" title="台积电将在美国开设芯片工厂">台积电将在美国开设芯片工厂</a></h3>
<h6 class="byline"> <span class="en_byline">DON CLARK</span>, <span class="en_byline">ANA SWANSON</span> <span class="time"></span> </h6>
